  "root_text": {
    "sn8.4:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 8.4 ",
    "sn8.4:0.2": "1. Vaṅgīsavagga ",
    "sn8.4:0.3": "Ānandasutta ",
    "sn8.4:1.1": "Ekaṁ samayaṁ āyasmā ānando sāvatthiyaṁ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
    "sn8.4:1.2": "Atha kho āyasmā ānando pubbaṇhasamayaṁ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṁ piṇḍāya pāvisi āyasmatā vaṅgīsena pacchāsamaṇena. ",
    "sn8.4:1.3": "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato vaṅgīsassa anabhirati uppannā hoti, rāgo cittaṁ anuddhaṁseti. ",
    "sn8.4:1.4": "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso āyasmantaṁ ānandaṁ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
    "sn8.4:2.1": "“Kāmarāgena ḍayhāmi, ",
    "sn8.4:2.2": "cittaṁ me pariḍayhati; ",
    "sn8.4:2.3": "Sādhu nibbāpanaṁ brūhi, ",
    "sn8.4:2.4": "anukampāya gotamā”ti. ",
    "sn8.4:3.1": "“Saññāya vipariyesā, ",
    "sn8.4:3.2": "cittaṁ te pariḍayhati; ",
    "sn8.4:3.3": "Nimittaṁ parivajjehi, ",
    "sn8.4:3.4": "subhaṁ rāgūpasaṁhitaṁ. ",
    "sn8.4:4.1": "Saṅkhāre parato passa, ",
    "sn8.4:4.2": "dukkhato mā ca attato; ",
    "sn8.4:4.3": "Nibbāpehi mahārāgaṁ, ",
    "sn8.4:4.4": "mā ḍayhittho punappunaṁ. ",
    "sn8.4:5.1": "Asubhāya cittaṁ bhāvehi, ",
    "sn8.4:5.2": "ekaggaṁ susamāhitaṁ; ",
    "sn8.4:5.3": "Sati kāyagatā tyatthu, ",
    "sn8.4:5.4": "nibbidābahulo bhava. ",
    "sn8.4:6.1": "Animittañca bhāvehi, ",
    "sn8.4:6.2": "mānānusayamujjaha; ",
    "sn8.4:6.3": "Tato mānābhisamayā, ",
    "sn8.4:6.4": "upasanto carissasī”ti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn8.4:0.1": "Linked Discourses 8.4 ",
    "sn8.4:0.2": "1. With Vaṅgīsa ",
    "sn8.4:0.3": "With Ānanda ",
    "sn8.4:1.1": "At one time Venerable Ānanda was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. ",
    "sn8.4:1.2": "Then Venerable Ānanda robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, entered Sāvatthī for alms with Venerable Vaṅgīsa as his second monk. ",
    "sn8.4:1.3": "And at that time Venerable Vaṅgīsa became dissatisfied, as lust infected his mind. ",
    "sn8.4:1.4": "Then he addressed Ānanda in verse: ",
    "sn8.4:2.1": "“I’ve got a burning desire for pleasure; ",
    "sn8.4:2.2": "My mind is on fire! ",
    "sn8.4:2.3": "Please, out of compassion, Gotama, ",
    "sn8.4:2.4": "tell me how to quench the flames.” ",
    "sn8.4:3.1": "“Your mind is on fire ",
    "sn8.4:3.2": "because of a perversion of perception. ",
    "sn8.4:3.3": "Turn away from the feature of things ",
    "sn8.4:3.4": "that’s attractive, provoking lust. ",
    "sn8.4:4.1": "See all conditioned phenomena as alien, ",
    "sn8.4:4.2": "as suffering and not-self. ",
    "sn8.4:4.3": "Extinguish the great fire of lust, ",
    "sn8.4:4.4": "don’t burn up again and again. ",
    "sn8.4:5.1": "With mind unified and serene, ",
    "sn8.4:5.2": "meditate on the ugly aspects of the body. ",
    "sn8.4:5.3": "With mindfulness immersed in the body, ",
    "sn8.4:5.4": "be full of disillusionment. ",
    "sn8.4:6.1": "Meditate on the signless, ",
    "sn8.4:6.2": "give up the underlying tendency to conceit; ",
    "sn8.4:6.3": "and when you comprehend conceit, ",
    "sn8.4:6.4": "you will live at peace.” "
  },
